      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我打算用两个section来区分：一个是\"Without Debounce\"，另一个是\"With Debounce (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\"。时间轴用毫秒单位，从0到1100毫秒左右，这样够吗？",
